UNIVERSAL WIDGET Privacy Policy - Version 2.1 (Build 1)

For Any Addition Questions You Can Reach Me On Twitter: @zacharyfurmanov

Universal Widget Collects User Data Such As;
- Analytics Data
- User Input Regarding Some Settings
- App Generated UUID
- Custom Text may be uploaded and is tied to your UUID, however, your UUID is in no way tied to you, your name, or any personal identifieble ID 

Your Name OR Personal ID Is Never Tied To Your Data

This Data Is Not Sold To Any Third Partys And Is Only Used For App Functionality and Testing

